|7 |            └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH LOCAL)|:EX10000|
|8 |              └─HASH DISTINCT                |        |
|9 |                └─PX BLOCK ITERATOR          |        |
|10|                  └─TABLE FULL SCAN          |t1      |
